                            <title xml:lang="ota" key="">شرائط اسلام</title>
                            <author key=""><persName xml:lang="ota-Latn-x-lc">some pieces in
                                    verse</persName></author>
                            <author key=""><persName xml:lang="ota-Latn-x-lc">prose on the same
                                    topics</persName></author>
                            <note>NOTE: This record has been automatically generated with minimal
                                modification from the corresponding entry in a printed catalogue. It
                                may contain errors. Please, consult the References section below for
                                more information.</note>
                            <note>A tract on the rites and observances in Islām. It begins: اسلام
                                بودر اسلامک شرط بشدر الخ. It ends on fol. 78a and is followed, on
                                ff. 78b-82b, by some pieces in verse and prose on the same topics,
                                and تفسیر فاتحه شريف, a Turkish commentary on the first sūra of the
                                Qur'ān, on fol. 79a.</note>
